---

---

<section class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-4">
  <div class="space-y-2 md:col-span-1">
    <h2 class="mb-6 text-4xl font-black tracking-tighter text-white uppercase">
      Operations
    </h2>
    <div
      class="data-border border-l-4 border-l-[var(--neon-cyan)] bg-[var(--neon-cyan)]/10 p-4"
    >
      <span class="mb-1 block font-bold text-[var(--neon-cyan)]"
        >01. MODELS</span
      >
      <p class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-400">
        Filter by capability, price, context. 85+ providers. RTFO indicators.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="data-border border-l-4 border-l-transparent bg-slate-900/30 p-4 transition-all hover:border-l-slate-400"
    >
      <span class="mb-1 block text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase"
        >02. Benchmarks</span
      >
      <p class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-400">
        H2H tables, scatter plots, radar charts. ~400 entries.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="data-border border-l-4 border-l-transparent bg-slate-900/30 p-4 transition-all hover:border-l-slate-400"
    >
      <span class="mb-1 block text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase"
        >03. Agents</span
      >
      <p class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-400">
        Version detection, GitHub releases, changelogs, service health.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="data-border border-l-4 border-l-transparent bg-slate-900/30 p-4 transition-all hover:border-l-slate-400"
    >
      <span class="mb-1 block text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase"
        >04. STATUS</span
      >
      <p class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-400">
        Live health for 22 providers. Incidents, maintenance, gauges.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="data-border flex flex-col items-center gap-8 bg-slate-900/50 p-8 md:col-span-3 md:flex-row"
  >
    <div class="data-border aspect-square w-full bg-black p-2 md:w-1/2">
      <img
        alt="models TUI interface"
        class="h-full w-full object-cover"
        src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}models-screenshot.png`}
      />
    </div>
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
      <p class="mb-6 text-2xl leading-tight font-light text-white">
        Real-time ingestion of 4,000+ model definitions across 85+ providers
        from models.dev.
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 font-mono text-xs text-[var(--neon-cyan)] uppercase">
        <li>+ Filter by capability and price</li>
        <li>+ Sort by date, cost, context</li>
        <li>+ Cross-provider search</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
